Text, images, styling and overall web design have been copied by Horstens Distribution, a moving company based in the Netherlands. 

Specifically, this site used HTTrack (you can see the code on their homepage here: ﻿<!-- Mirrored from www.mattsmoving.com/ by HTTrack Website Copier/3.x [XR&CO'2010], Fri, 15 Jul 2011 08:17:50 GMT -->) to mirror our site. This copying even includes our Google Analytics code (which is affecting our ability to use Analytics to accurately track our business, as Horsten's traffic and referrals are showing up in our account).
